snippet.title: Shize™️ Heritage Collection Advert
snippet.description:
Here at Shize LLC, we pour our hearts and souls into every product. In honor of the Shize family, we’re excited to announce the new Heritage 2020 Collection!

We’re bringing back every flavor since our flagship taste from 1744. It’s time to enjoy Cherry Pop, Gamer Energy, Pineapple Pizza, and so many more at your local grocer.

Our cans have so much personality, and you’re sure to find a favorite. See our collection today - they’ll be waiting for you!

https://oxyoxspring.itch.io/onlycans
